    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >准备好在《大厨的轮班》中掀起一场烹饪风暴 - 这是一个快节奏的打字游戏，设定在繁忙的餐厅里！以你的键盘为武器，你需要在顾客失去耐心之前烹饪并为他们提供美味的菜肴。但这还不是全部 - 你还需要应对各种疯狂的干扰，从老鼠入侵到难以驾驭的顾客。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>期待什么</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 1茶匙 <strong>混乱，快节奏</strong> 的游戏玩法 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 1包易学难精通的<strong>打字</strong>机制 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 1杯有趣的<strong>时间管理</strong>元素 </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>所有操作都通过键入</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2390230/extras/0b2e767f6bb2c482ac98ffa24497a4b7.poster.avif?t=1771582923\" width=600 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2390230/extras/0b2e767f6bb2c482ac98ffa24497a4b7.webm?t=1771582923\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2390230/extras/0b2e767f6bb2c482ac98ffa24497a4b7.mp4?t=1771582923\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >而且我们是认真的！</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 通过打字浏览菜单</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 通过打字准备和为顾客服务</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 通过打字选择对话选项</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><br><strong>6 家风味各异的餐厅！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2390230/extras/ac6ca3aac8cbb210f80699e58b07fc97.avif?t=1771582923\" width=616 height=118 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >踏上一场穿越6个生动章节的烹饪之旅，品味世界各地多样的美食风味，每家餐厅都代表着不同的饮食文化，提出不同的怪癖和挑战。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><br><strong>丰富多彩的角色</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2390230/extras/6bccdac05f7fc0969020d5c53b720c94.avif?t=1771582923\" width=616 height=177 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在游戏中，你将遇到各种各样的角色，从拥有自己个性的顾客到推动故事发展的角色。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2390230/extras/38621430eb911316942d2e43e05e6ff1.webp?t=1771582923\" width=616 height=49 /></span></p>",
